# Bitcoin Retirement Forecast — optional environment overrides.
#
# The application runs KEYLESS by design (ST7 §7): no CoinGecko key is ever
# required, neither for tests nor for the released version. The hook below is a
# convenience for contributors who want to use their own CoinGecko Demo key.
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and uncomment to use. Never commit `.env`.

# Optional CoinGecko Demo API key. When set, the client targets
# pro-api.coingecko.com and sends the `x-cg-demo-api-key` header.
# Leave unset for standard keyless operation.
# COINGECKO_API_KEY=

# Optional local port override (default 8000, with incremental bind fallback).
# BTC_FORECAST_PORT=8000
